Key Match Events: Netherlands defeated Namibia in a nervy game
Scott Edwards led Netherlands to two consecutive wins
Post-Match Reflections: Scott Edwards: 'It's well and truly in our hands'
Bas de Leede: 'The self-belief has always been there'
Miscellaneous Highlights: Netherlands need to win their final outing against Sri Lanka to secure their spot in the Super-12
Others: Bas de Leede was adjudged the man of the match for his two wickets and his fighting 30 off 30 balls
Vikramjeet Singh and Max O'Dowd gave a good start to the team
